OL,3,CTeenager given referral order after
OL,4,Cstarting a fire at London Oratory
OL,5,CSchool
OL,7,FA 16-year-old boy who started a fire
OL,8,Fat a prestigious Catholic school in
OL,9,Fwest London, which caused around #2
OL,10,Fmillion worth of damage has been given
OL,11,Fa referral order for 10 months.
OL,13,FA major incident was declared after
OL,14,Fsmoke and orange flames broke out in
OL,15,Fthe atrium of the London Oratory
OL,16,FSchool in Fulham on December 27 last
OL,17,Fyear.
