OL,3,CTeenager given referral order after
OL,4,Cstarting a fire at London Oratory
OL,5,CSchool
OL,7,FThe fire was on the 4th floor of the
OL,8,Fschool library. The building and
OL,9,Fsurrounding area had to be evacuated,
OL,10,FAngela Mahadeo, prosecuting, told
OL,11,FWimbledon Magistrates' Court on
OL,12,FTuesday.
OL,14,FWhen the defendant was interviewed by
OL,15,Fpolice, he gave a prepared statement
OL,16,Fin which he said he got on to the roof
OL,17,Fand started smoking. Some ash then
OL,18,Fwent on to a piece of paper, which
OL,19,Fwent on to other pieces of paper, Ms
OL,20,FMahadeo added.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
