OL,5,CSchool
OL,7,FEdward Fenner, defending, said the
OL,8,Fyouth went to the school "seeking to
OL,9,Fcommit suicide".
OL,11,FA statement from the school's
OL,12,Fheadmaster Daniel Wright, which was
OL,13,Fwritten in May, was read out by Ms
OL,14,FMahadeo. The statement said that the
OL,15,Fcost of the damage at that point was
OL,16,Fin the region of #2 million.
OL,18,FHe said more than 1,000 pupils missed
OL,19,Ffive days of on-site education
OL,20,Ffollowing the incident, and 360 pupils
OL,21,Fmissed 13 days.
