OL,5,CSchool
OL,7,FMr Wright said: "This incident has
OL,8,Fcaused serious disruption to the
OL,9,Fschool. The staff have been saddened
OL,10,Fby the fire and morale was low. It's
OL,11,Ftoo early to say whether the fire will
OL,12,Faffect staff turnover.
OL,14,F"The fire was a very public event
OL,15,Freported in the national news. It
OL,16,Fcan't reflect well on the reputation
OL,17,Fof this prestigious school."
