OL,7,FThe youth, who cannot be named because
OL,8,Fof his age, was arrested by police on
OL,9,Fthe same day and initially denied a
OL,10,Fcharge of arson before later pleading
OL,11,Fguilty to the offence on September 2.
OL,13,FHe was also charged with arson with
OL,14,Frecklessness for endangering life and
OL,15,Fassaulting an emergency worker ` and
OL,16,Fdenied both offences.
