OL,7,FThe judge ruled the defendant's
OL,8,Fbehaviour towards the officer was
OL,9,F"reckless" and found him guilty of
OL,10,Fassaulting an emergency worker last
OL,11,Fmonth.
OL,13,FMr Fenner said the defendant is of
OL,14,Fgood character and had a depressive
OL,15,Fepisode at the time of the offences.
OL,17,FThe defendant told the judge: "I am
OL,18,Fsorry and I'm not the same person that
OL,19,FI was a year ago."
