OL,7,FAs well as the defendant's referral
OL,8,Forder for 10 months, the teenager was
OL,9,Falso ordered to pay #100 compensation
OL,10,Fto the police officer and a #26 victim
OL,11,Fsurcharge.
OL,13,FMr Sweet said: "A lot of damage was
OL,14,Fcaused and a lot of disruption. You
OL,15,Fknew that the school was not occupied,
OL,16,Fthat was one of the factors I took
OL,17,Finto account when I heard the trial
OL,18,Fabout endangering life."
